        $useful_links = array(
            array('id' => '1','type' => 'PRIVACY_POLICY','title' => '{"language":{"en":{"title":"Privacy Policy"},"fr":{"title":"Politique de Confidentialit\\u00e9"},"es":{"title":"Pol\\u00edtica de Privacidad"},"ar":{"title":"\\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0633\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062e\\u0635\\u0648\\u0635\\u064a\\u0629"}}}','slug' => 'privacy-policy','url' => 'privacy-policy','content' => '{"language":{"en":{"content":"<p>Welcome to CarBo! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our website, mobile app, and related services. By accessing or using CarBo, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.<br><strong>1. Information We Collect<\\/strong><br><strong>1.1 Personal Information<\\/strong><br>When you register, book a car, or list a vehicle, we may collect:<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ul style=\\"list-style-type:none;\\"><li>Name, email, phone number, and address<\\/li><li>Payment details (processed securely via third-party gateways)<\\/li><li>Government-issued ID for verification (if required)<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>1.2 Non-Personal Information<\\/strong><br>We collect data such as:<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ul style=\\"list-style-type:none;\\"><li>IP address and device information<\\/li><li>Browser type and operating system<\\/li><li>Usage data (e.g., pages visited, time spent on platform)<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>1.3 Payment Information<\\/strong><br>CarBo integrates multiple payment gateways (PayPal, CoinGate, QRPay, Tatum, Stripe, Flutterwave, SSLCOMMERZ, Razorpay, Perfect Money). We do not store or process payment details directly\\u2014transactions are handled securely by these providers.<br><strong>2. How We Use Your Information<\\/strong><br>We use your information to:<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ul style=\\"list-style-type:none;\\"><li>Facilitate car bookings and vendor management<\\/li><li>Improve our platform and user experience<\\/li><li>Process payments and verify transactions<\\/li><li>Send important updates, promotions, and notifications<\\/li><li>Ensure security and prevent fraudulent activities<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>3. Sharing Your Information<\\/strong><br>We do not sell or rent your personal data. However, we may share information with:<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ul style=\\"list-style-type:none;\\"><li><strong>Vendors &amp; Users:<\\/strong> To complete bookings and transactions<\\/li><li><strong>Payment Processors:<\\/strong> To handle secure transactions<\\/li><li><strong>Legal Authorities:<\\/strong> If required by law or to protect our platform<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>4. Data Security<\\/strong><br>We use encryption, firewalls, and secure servers to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, so we encourage safe browsing practices.<br><strong>5. Cookies &amp; Tracking Technologies<\\/strong><br>CarBo uses cookies to enhance your experience, remember preferences, and analyze site traffic. You can adjust cookie settings in your browser.<br><strong>6. Third-Party Links<\\/strong><br>Our platform may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy policies or content.<br><strong>7. Your Rights &amp; Choices<\\/strong><br>You have the right to:<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ul style=\\"list-style-type:none;\\"><li>Access, update, or delete your personal data<\\/li><li>Opt out of marketing emails<\\/li><li>Disable cookies through browser settings<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>8. Changes to This Policy<\\/strong><br>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify users of major changes via email or platform announcements.<br><strong>9. Contact Us<\\/strong><br>For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, contact us at:<br><img class=\\"image_resized\\" style=\\"width:22px;\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/a.slack-edge.com\\/production-standard-emoji-assets\\/14.0\\/google-medium\\/1f4e7@2x.png\\" alt=\\":e-mail:\\"> <a href=\\"mailto:support@carbo.com\\">support@carbo.com<\\/a><br><img class=\\"image_resized\\" style=\\"width:22px;\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/a.slack-edge.com\\/production-standard-emoji-assets\\/14.0\\/google-medium\\/1f4cd@2x.png\\" alt=\\":round_pushpin:\\"> 123 CarBo Street, Cityville, Country<\\/p>"},"fr":{"content":"<p>Bienvenue sur CarBo ! Votre vie priv\\u00e9e est importante pour nous. Cette Politique de Confidentialit\\u00e9 explique comment nous collectons, utilisons, divulguons et prot\\u00e9geons vos informations lorsque vous utilisez notre site web, notre application mobile et nos services associ\\u00e9s. En acc\\u00e9dant ou en utilisant CarBo, vous acceptez les termes de cette Politique de Confidentialit\\u00e9.<\\/p><h4><strong>1. Informations que nous collectons<\\/strong><\\/h4><p><strong>1.1 Informations personnelles<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Lorsque vous vous inscrivez, r\\u00e9servez une voiture ou mettez un v\\u00e9hicule en ligne, nous pouvons collecter :<\\/p><ul><li>Nom, email, num\\u00e9ro de t\\u00e9l\\u00e9phone et adresse<\\/li><li>D\\u00e9tails de paiement (trait\\u00e9s en toute s\\u00e9curit\\u00e9 via des passerelles tierces)<\\/li><li>Pi\\u00e8ce d\\u2019identit\\u00e9 officielle pour v\\u00e9rification (si n\\u00e9cessaire)<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>1.2 Informations non personnelles<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Nous collectons des donn\\u00e9es telles que :<\\/p><ul><li>Adresse IP et informations sur l\\u2019appareil<\\/li><li>Type de navigateur et syst\\u00e8me d\\u2019exploitation<\\/li><li>Donn\\u00e9es d\\u2019utilisation (ex. : pages visit\\u00e9es, temps pass\\u00e9 sur la plateforme)<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>1.3 Informations de paiement<\\/strong><\\/p><p>CarBo int\\u00e8gre plusieurs passerelles de paiement (PayPal, CoinGate, QRPay, Tatum, Stripe, Flutterwave, SSLCOMMERZ, Razorpay, Perfect Money). Nous ne stockons ni ne traitons directement les d\\u00e9tails de paiement\\u2014les transactions sont g\\u00e9r\\u00e9es en toute s\\u00e9curit\\u00e9 par ces fournisseurs.<\\/p><h4><strong>2. Comment nous utilisons vos informations<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Nous utilisons vos informations pour :<\\/p><ul><li>Faciliter les r\\u00e9servations de voitures et la gestion des vendeurs<\\/li><li>Am\\u00e9liorer notre plateforme et l\\u2019exp\\u00e9rience utilisateur<\\/li><li>Traiter les paiements et v\\u00e9rifier les transactions<\\/li><li>Envoyer des mises \\u00e0 jour importantes, des promotions et des notifications<\\/li><li>Assurer la s\\u00e9curit\\u00e9 et pr\\u00e9venir les activit\\u00e9s frauduleuses<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>3. Partage de vos informations<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Nous ne vendons ni ne louons vos donn\\u00e9es personnelles. Cependant, nous pouvons partager des informations avec :<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Vendeurs &amp; Utilisateurs :<\\/strong> Pour compl\\u00e9ter les r\\u00e9servations et transactions<\\/li><li><strong>Processeurs de paiement :<\\/strong> Pour g\\u00e9rer les transactions s\\u00e9curis\\u00e9es<\\/li><li><strong>Autorit\\u00e9s l\\u00e9gales :<\\/strong> Si la loi l\\u2019exige ou pour prot\\u00e9ger notre plateforme<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>4. S\\u00e9curit\\u00e9 des donn\\u00e9es<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Nous utilisons le chiffrement, des pare-feux et des serveurs s\\u00e9curis\\u00e9s pour prot\\u00e9ger vos donn\\u00e9es. Cependant, aucune m\\u00e9thode de transmission sur Internet n\\u2019est 100 % s\\u00e9curis\\u00e9e, nous vous encourageons donc \\u00e0 adopter des pratiques de navigation s\\u00fbres.<\\/p><h4><strong>5. Cookies &amp; Technologies de suivi<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>CarBo utilise des cookies pour am\\u00e9liorer votre exp\\u00e9rience, m\\u00e9moriser vos pr\\u00e9f\\u00e9rences et analyser le trafic du site. Vous pouvez ajuster les param\\u00e8tres des cookies dans votre navigateur.<\\/p><h4><strong>6. Liens vers des sites tiers<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Notre plateforme peut contenir des liens vers des sites web tiers. Nous ne sommes pas responsables de leurs politiques de confidentialit\\u00e9 ou de leur contenu.<\\/p><h4><strong>7. Vos droits &amp; choix<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Vous avez le droit de :<\\/p><ul><li>Acc\\u00e9der, mettre \\u00e0 jour ou supprimer vos donn\\u00e9es personnelles<\\/li><li>Vous d\\u00e9sinscrire des emails marketing<\\/li><li>D\\u00e9sactiver les cookies via les param\\u00e8tres du navigateur<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>8. Modifications de cette Politique<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Nous pouvons mettre \\u00e0 jour cette Politique de Confidentialit\\u00e9 p\\u00e9riodiquement. Nous informerons les utilisateurs des modifications majeures par email ou via des annonces sur la plateforme.<\\/p><h4><strong>9. Contactez-nous<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Pour toute question concernant cette Politique de Confidentialit\\u00e9, contactez-nous \\u00e0 :<br>\\ud83d\\udce7 <strong>support@carbo.com<\\/strong><br>\\ud83d\\udccd <strong>123 CarBo Street, Cityville, Country<\\/strong><\\/p>"},"es":{"content":"<p>\\u00a1Bienvenido a CarBo! Tu privacidad es importante para nosotros. Esta Pol\\u00edtica de Privacidad explica c\\u00f3mo recopilamos, usamos, divulgamos y protegemos tu informaci\\u00f3n cuando utilizas nuestro sitio web, aplicaci\\u00f3n m\\u00f3vil y servicios relacionados. Al acceder o utilizar CarBo, aceptas los t\\u00e9rminos de esta Pol\\u00edtica de Privacidad.<\\/p><h4><strong>1. Informaci\\u00f3n que recopilamos<\\/strong><\\/h4><p><strong>1.1 Informaci\\u00f3n personal<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Cuando te registras, reservas un coche o publicas un veh\\u00edculo, podemos recopilar:<\\/p><ul><li>Nombre, correo electr\\u00f3nico, n\\u00famero de tel\\u00e9fono y direcci\\u00f3n<\\/li><li>Datos de pago (procesados de forma segura a trav\\u00e9s de pasarelas de pago de terceros)<\\/li><li>Identificaci\\u00f3n oficial para verificaci\\u00f3n (si es necesario)<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>1.2 Informaci\\u00f3n no personal<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Recopilamos datos como:<\\/p><ul><li>Direcci\\u00f3n IP e informaci\\u00f3n del dispositivo<\\/li><li>Tipo de navegador y sistema operativo<\\/li><li>Datos de uso (por ejemplo, p\\u00e1ginas visitadas, tiempo en la plataforma)<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>1.3 Informaci\\u00f3n de pago<\\/strong><\\/p><p>CarBo integra m\\u00faltiples pasarelas de pago (PayPal, CoinGate, QRPay, Tatum, Stripe, Flutterwave, SSLCOMMERZ, Razorpay, Perfect Money). No almacenamos ni procesamos los detalles de pago directamente\\u2014las transacciones son gestionadas de forma segura por estos proveedores.<\\/p><h4><strong>2. C\\u00f3mo usamos tu informaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Utilizamos tu informaci\\u00f3n para:<\\/p><ul><li>Facilitar las reservas de coches y la gesti\\u00f3n de vendedores<\\/li><li>Mejorar nuestra plataforma y la experiencia del usuario<\\/li><li>Procesar pagos y verificar transacciones<\\/li><li>Enviar actualizaciones importantes, promociones y notificaciones<\\/li><li>Garantizar la seguridad y prevenir actividades fraudulentas<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>3. Compartir tu informaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>No vendemos ni alquilamos tus datos personales. Sin embargo, podemos compartir informaci\\u00f3n con:<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Vendedores y usuarios:<\\/strong> Para completar reservas y transacciones<\\/li><li><strong>Procesadores de pago:<\\/strong> Para gestionar transacciones seguras<\\/li><li><strong>Autoridades legales:<\\/strong> Si lo exige la ley o para proteger nuestra plataforma<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>4. Seguridad de los datos<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Utilizamos cifrado, firewalls y servidores seguros para proteger tus datos. Sin embargo, ninguna transmisi\\u00f3n por Internet es 100 % segura, por lo que te recomendamos pr\\u00e1cticas de navegaci\\u00f3n seguras.<\\/p><h4><strong>5. Cookies y Tecnolog\\u00edas de seguimiento<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>CarBo usa cookies para mejorar tu experiencia, recordar preferencias y analizar el tr\\u00e1fico del sitio. Puedes ajustar la configuraci\\u00f3n de cookies en tu navegador.<\\/p><h4><strong>6. Enlaces a terceros<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Nuestra plataforma puede contener enlaces a sitios web de terceros. No somos responsables de sus pol\\u00edticas de privacidad ni de su contenido.<\\/p><h4><strong>7. Tus derechos y opciones<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Tienes derecho a:<\\/p><ul><li>Acceder, actualizar o eliminar tus datos personales<\\/li><li>Optar por no recibir correos electr\\u00f3nicos de marketing<\\/li><li>Deshabilitar cookies a trav\\u00e9s de la configuraci\\u00f3n del navegador<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>8. Cambios en esta Pol\\u00edtica<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Podemos actualizar esta Pol\\u00edtica de Privacidad peri\\u00f3dicamente. Notificaremos a los usuarios sobre cambios importantes por correo electr\\u00f3nico o anuncios en la plataforma.<\\/p><h4><strong>9. Cont\\u00e1ctanos<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Si tienes preguntas sobre esta Pol\\u00edtica de Privacidad, cont\\u00e1ctanos en:<br>\\ud83d\\udce7 <strong>support@carbo.com<\\/strong><br>\\ud83d\\udccd <strong>123 CarBo Street, Cityville, Country<\\/strong><\\/p>"},"ar":{"content":"<p>\\u0645\\u0631\\u062d\\u0628\\u064b\\u0627 \\u0628\\u0643 \\u0641\\u064a CarBo! \\u0646\\u062d\\u0646 \\u0646\\u0648\\u0644\\u064a \\u062e\\u0635\\u0648\\u0635\\u064a\\u062a\\u0643 \\u0623\\u0647\\u0645\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0643\\u0628\\u064a\\u0631\\u0629. \\u062a\\u0648\\u0636\\u062d \\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0633\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062e\\u0635\\u0648\\u0635\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0647\\u0630\\u0647 \\u0643\\u064a\\u0641\\u064a\\u0629 \\u062c\\u0645\\u0639 \\u0645\\u0639\\u0644\\u0648\\u0645\\u0627\\u062a\\u0643 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u062e\\u062f\\u0627\\u0645\\u0647\\u0627 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0643\\u0634\\u0641 \\u0639\\u0646\\u0647\\u0627 \\u0648\\u062d\\u0645\\u0627\\u064a\\u062a\\u0647\\u0627 \\u0639\\u0646\\u062f \\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u062e\\u062f\\u0627\\u0645 \\u0645\\u0648\\u0642\\u0639\\u0646\\u0627 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0625\\u0644\\u0643\\u062a\\u0631\\u0648\\u0646\\u064a \\u0648\\u062a\\u0637\\u0628\\u064a\\u0642\\u0646\\u0627 \\u0648\\u062e\\u062f\\u0645\\u0627\\u062a\\u0646\\u0627 \\u0630\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0635\\u0644\\u0629. \\u0628\\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u062e\\u062f\\u0627\\u0645\\u0643 CarBo\\u060c \\u0641\\u0625\\u0646\\u0643 \\u062a\\u0648\\u0627\\u0641\\u0642 \\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0634\\u0631\\u0648\\u0637 \\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0633\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062e\\u0635\\u0648\\u0635\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0647\\u0630\\u0647.<\\/p><h4><strong>1. \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0639\\u0644\\u0648\\u0645\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u064a \\u0646\\u062c\\u0645\\u0639\\u0647\\u0627<\\/strong><\\/h4><p><strong>1.1 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0639\\u0644\\u0648\\u0645\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0634\\u062e\\u0635\\u064a\\u0629<\\/strong><\\/p><p>\\u0639\\u0646\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0633\\u062c\\u064a\\u0644 \\u0623\\u0648 \\u062d\\u062c\\u0632 \\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0631\\u0629 \\u0623\\u0648 \\u0625\\u062f\\u0631\\u0627\\u062c \\u0645\\u0631\\u0643\\u0628\\u0629\\u060c \\u0642\\u062f \\u0646\\u0642\\u0648\\u0645 \\u0628\\u062c\\u0645\\u0639:<\\/p><ul><li>\\u0627\\u0644\\u0627\\u0633\\u0645\\u060c \\u0627\\u0644\\u0628\\u0631\\u064a\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u0625\\u0644\\u0643\\u062a\\u0631\\u0648\\u0646\\u064a\\u060c \\u0631\\u0642\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0647\\u0627\\u062a\\u0641\\u060c \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0639\\u0646\\u0648\\u0627\\u0646<\\/li><li>\\u062a\\u0641\\u0627\\u0635\\u064a\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062f\\u0641\\u0639 (\\u062a\\u062a\\u0645 \\u0645\\u0639\\u0627\\u0644\\u062c\\u062a\\u0647\\u0627 \\u0628\\u0623\\u0645\\u0627\\u0646 \\u0639\\u0628\\u0631 \\u0628\\u0648\\u0627\\u0628\\u0627\\u062a \\u062f\\u0641\\u0639 \\u0637\\u0631\\u0641 \\u062b\\u0627\\u0644\\u062b)<\\/li><li>\\u0628\\u0637\\u0627\\u0642\\u0629 \\u0647\\u0648\\u064a\\u0629 \\u062d\\u0643\\u0648\\u0645\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0644\\u0644\\u062a\\u062d\\u0642\\u0642 (\\u0625\\u0630\\u0627 \\u0644\\u0632\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u0645\\u0631)<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>1.2 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0639\\u0644\\u0648\\u0645\\u0627\\u062a \\u063a\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0634\\u062e\\u0635\\u064a\\u0629<\\/strong><\\/p><p>\\u0646\\u062c\\u0645\\u0639 \\u0628\\u064a\\u0627\\u0646\\u0627\\u062a \\u0645\\u062b\\u0644:<\\/p><ul><li>\\u0639\\u0646\\u0648\\u0627\\u0646 IP \\u0648\\u0645\\u0639\\u0644\\u0648\\u0645\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u062c\\u0647\\u0627\\u0632<\\/li><li>\\u0646\\u0648\\u0639 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u062a\\u0635\\u0641\\u062d \\u0648\\u0646\\u0638\\u0627\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0634\\u063a\\u064a\\u0644<\\/li><li>\\u0628\\u064a\\u0627\\u0646\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u062e\\u062f\\u0627\\u0645 (\\u0645\\u062b\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0635\\u0641\\u062d\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u064a \\u062a\\u0645\\u062a \\u0632\\u064a\\u0627\\u0631\\u062a\\u0647\\u0627 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0648\\u0642\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u062a\\u063a\\u0631\\u0642 \\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0646\\u0635\\u0629)<\\/li><\\/ul><p>\\ud83d\\udce7 <strong>support@carbo.com<\\/strong><br>\\ud83d\\udccd <strong>123 CarBo Street, Cityville, Country<\\/strong><\\/p>"}}}','status' => '1','editable' => '0','created_at' => '2023-07-31 12:02:44','updated_at' => '2025-02-21 09:49:21'),
  array('id' => '2','type' => 'UNKNOWN','title' => '{"language":{"en":{"title":"Refund Policy"},"fr":{"title":"Politique de Remboursement"},"es":{"title":"Pol\\u00edtica de Reembolsos"},"ar":{"title":"\\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0633\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u0631\\u062f\\u0627\\u062f"}}}','slug' => 'refund-policy','url' => 'refund-policy','content' => '{"language":{"en":{"content":"<p><strong>Refund Policy<\\/strong><br>At CarBo, we strive to provide a seamless and reliable car booking experience for both users and vendors. This Refund Policy outlines the conditions under which refunds may be issued for bookings made through our platform. By using CarBo, you agree to this policy.<strong>1. Eligibility for Refunds<\\/strong><br>Refunds are applicable under the following conditions:<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ul style=\\"list-style-type:none;\\"><li><strong>Booking Cancellation by Vendor:<\\/strong> If a vendor cancels a confirmed booking, the user is eligible for a full refund.<\\/li><li><strong>Unavailability of Vehicle:<\\/strong> If the booked vehicle is unavailable at the scheduled time and no suitable replacement is provided, the user may request a refund.<\\/li><li><strong>Payment Errors:<\\/strong> In cases of duplicate payments or incorrect charges due to system errors, users can request a refund.<\\/li><li><strong>Failed Transaction:<\\/strong> If a user\\u2019s payment is deducted, but the booking is not confirmed, a refund will be processed.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>2. Non-Refundable Cases<\\/strong><br>Refunds will not be issued in the following situations:<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ul style=\\"list-style-type:none;\\"><li><strong>User-Initiated Cancellations:<\\/strong> If a user cancels a confirmed booking, the refund policy will depend on the vendor\\u2019s cancellation terms.<\\/li><li><strong>Late Cancellations:<\\/strong> Cancellations made within the restricted time frame (as defined by the vendor) may not be eligible for a refund.<\\/li><li><strong>No-Show:<\\/strong> If a user fails to pick up the vehicle at the scheduled time without prior cancellation, no refund will be provided.<\\/li><li><strong>Completed Rides:<\\/strong> Once a booking has been successfully completed, refunds are not applicable.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>3. Refund Processing Time<\\/strong><br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ul style=\\"list-style-type:none;\\"><li>Approved refunds will be processed within <strong>7-14 business days<\\/strong> to the original payment method.<\\/li><li>Refund times may vary based on the payment gateway used (PayPal, CoinGate, QRPay, Tatum, Stripe, Flutterwave, SSLCOMMERZ, Razorpay, Perfect Money).<\\/li><li>Users will receive a confirmation email once the refund has been processed.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>4. How to Request a Refund<\\/strong><br>To request a refund, users must:<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><ol style=\\"list-style-type:decimal;\\"><li>Contact our support team via <strong>[Your Support Email]<\\/strong> within <strong>[X] days<\\/strong> of the booking date.<\\/li><li>Provide the booking reference number and a valid reason for the refund request.<\\/li><li>If applicable, attach supporting documents (e.g., proof of incorrect charges or unavailability of the vehicle).<\\/li><\\/ol><p>Our team will review the request and respond within <strong>[X] business days<\\/strong>.<strong>5. Changes to This Policy<\\/strong><br>CarBo reserves the right to modify or update this refund policy at any time. Any changes will be communicated via email or platform notifications.<strong>6. Contact Us<\\/strong><br>For any refund-related inquiries, please reach out to us at:<br><img class=\\"image_resized\\" style=\\"width:22px;\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/a.slack-edge.com\\/production-standard-emoji-assets\\/14.0\\/google-medium\\/1f4e7@2x.png\\" alt=\\":e-mail:\\"> <a href=\\"mailto:support@carbo.com\\">support@carbo.com<\\/a><br><img class=\\"image_resized\\" style=\\"width:22px;\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/a.slack-edge.com\\/production-standard-emoji-assets\\/14.0\\/google-medium\\/1f4cd@2x.png\\" alt=\\":round_pushpin:\\"> 123 CarBo Street, Cityville, Country<\\/p>"},"fr":{"content":"<p>Chez CarBo, nous nous effor\\u00e7ons d\'offrir une exp\\u00e9rience de r\\u00e9servation de voiture fluide et fiable aux utilisateurs et aux vendeurs. Cette Politique de Remboursement d\\u00e9crit les conditions dans lesquelles des remboursements peuvent \\u00eatre accord\\u00e9s pour les r\\u00e9servations effectu\\u00e9es via notre plateforme. En utilisant CarBo, vous acceptez cette politique.<\\/p><h4><strong>1. Admissibilit\\u00e9 aux Remboursements<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Les remboursements sont applicables dans les cas suivants :<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Annulation par le vendeur :<\\/strong> Si un vendeur annule une r\\u00e9servation confirm\\u00e9e, l\'utilisateur a droit \\u00e0 un remboursement int\\u00e9gral.<\\/li><li><strong>Indisponibilit\\u00e9 du v\\u00e9hicule :<\\/strong> Si le v\\u00e9hicule r\\u00e9serv\\u00e9 n\'est pas disponible \\u00e0 l\'heure pr\\u00e9vue et qu\'aucun remplacement appropri\\u00e9 n\'est propos\\u00e9, l\'utilisateur peut demander un remboursement.<\\/li><li><strong>Erreurs de paiement :<\\/strong> En cas de paiements en double ou de frais incorrects dus \\u00e0 des erreurs du syst\\u00e8me, les utilisateurs peuvent demander un remboursement.<\\/li><li><strong>Transaction \\u00e9chou\\u00e9e :<\\/strong> Si un paiement est d\\u00e9bit\\u00e9, mais que la r\\u00e9servation n\'est pas confirm\\u00e9e, un remboursement sera trait\\u00e9.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>2. Cas Non Remboursables<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Aucun remboursement ne sera accord\\u00e9 dans les situations suivantes :<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Annulations initi\\u00e9es par l\'utilisateur :<\\/strong> Si un utilisateur annule une r\\u00e9servation confirm\\u00e9e, la politique de remboursement d\\u00e9pendra des conditions d\'annulation du vendeur.<\\/li><li><strong>Annulations tardives :<\\/strong> Les annulations effectu\\u00e9es dans le d\\u00e9lai restreint (d\\u00e9fini par le vendeur) peuvent ne pas \\u00eatre \\u00e9ligibles \\u00e0 un remboursement.<\\/li><li><strong>Absence de l\'utilisateur :<\\/strong> Si un utilisateur ne r\\u00e9cup\\u00e8re pas le v\\u00e9hicule \\u00e0 l\'heure convenue sans annulation pr\\u00e9alable, aucun remboursement ne sera accord\\u00e9.<\\/li><li><strong>Trajets termin\\u00e9s :<\\/strong> Une fois la r\\u00e9servation compl\\u00e9t\\u00e9e avec succ\\u00e8s, aucun remboursement n\'est applicable.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>3. D\\u00e9lai de Traitement du Remboursement<\\/strong><\\/h4><ul><li>Les remboursements approuv\\u00e9s seront trait\\u00e9s dans un d\\u00e9lai de <strong>7 \\u00e0 14 jours ouvrables<\\/strong> vers le mode de paiement d\'origine.<\\/li><li>Les d\\u00e9lais de remboursement peuvent varier en fonction du prestataire de paiement utilis\\u00e9 (PayPal, CoinGate, QRPay, Tatum, Stripe, Flutterwave, SSLCOMMERZ, Razorpay, Perfect Money).<\\/li><li>Un email de confirmation sera envoy\\u00e9 une fois le remboursement effectu\\u00e9.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>4. Comment Demander un Remboursement<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Pour demander un remboursement, les utilisateurs doivent :<\\/p><ul><li>Contacter notre \\u00e9quipe d\'assistance \\u00e0 l\'adresse <strong>[Votre Email de Support]<\\/strong> dans un d\\u00e9lai de <strong>[X] jours<\\/strong> apr\\u00e8s la date de r\\u00e9servation.<\\/li><li>Fournir le num\\u00e9ro de r\\u00e9servation et une raison valide pour la demande de remboursement.<\\/li><li>Joindre, si n\\u00e9cessaire, des documents justificatifs (ex. : preuve de frais incorrects ou d\'indisponibilit\\u00e9 du v\\u00e9hicule).<\\/li><li>Notre \\u00e9quipe examinera la demande et r\\u00e9pondra dans un d\\u00e9lai de <strong>[X] jours ouvrables<\\/strong>.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>5. Modifications de Cette Politique<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>CarBo se r\\u00e9serve le droit de modifier ou de mettre \\u00e0 jour cette politique de remboursement \\u00e0 tout moment. Toute modification sera communiqu\\u00e9e par email ou via des notifications sur la plateforme.<\\/p><h4><strong>6. Contactez-nous<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Pour toute question li\\u00e9e aux remboursements, veuillez nous contacter \\u00e0 :<br>\\ud83d\\udce7 <strong>support@carbo.com<\\/strong><br>\\ud83d\\udccd <strong>123 CarBo Street, Cityville, Country<\\/strong><\\/p>"},"es":{"content":"<p>En CarBo, nos esforzamos por ofrecer una experiencia de reserva de autos fluida y confiable para usuarios y vendedores. Esta Pol\\u00edtica de Reembolsos describe las condiciones bajo las cuales se pueden emitir reembolsos por reservas realizadas a trav\\u00e9s de nuestra plataforma. Al usar CarBo, aceptas esta pol\\u00edtica.<\\/p><h4><strong>1. Elegibilidad para Reembolsos<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Los reembolsos aplican en los siguientes casos:<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Cancelaci\\u00f3n por parte del vendedor:<\\/strong> Si un vendedor cancela una reserva confirmada, el usuario tiene derecho a un reembolso completo.<\\/li><li><strong>Indisponibilidad del veh\\u00edculo:<\\/strong> Si el veh\\u00edculo reservado no est\\u00e1 disponible a la hora programada y no se ofrece un reemplazo adecuado, el usuario puede solicitar un reembolso.<\\/li><li><strong>Errores de pago:<\\/strong> En caso de pagos duplicados o cargos incorrectos debido a errores del sistema, los usuarios pueden solicitar un reembolso.<\\/li><li><strong>Transacci\\u00f3n fallida:<\\/strong> Si se deduce un pago, pero la reserva no se confirma, se procesar\\u00e1 un reembolso.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>2. Casos No Reembolsables<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>No se emitir\\u00e1n reembolsos en las siguientes situaciones:<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Cancelaciones iniciadas por el usuario:<\\/strong> Si un usuario cancela una reserva confirmada, la pol\\u00edtica de reembolso depender\\u00e1 de las condiciones del vendedor.<\\/li><li><strong>Cancelaciones tard\\u00edas:<\\/strong> Cancelaciones realizadas dentro del per\\u00edodo restringido (seg\\u00fan lo definido por el vendedor) pueden no ser elegibles para reembolso.<\\/li><li><strong>No presentaci\\u00f3n:<\\/strong> Si un usuario no recoge el veh\\u00edculo a la hora programada sin una cancelaci\\u00f3n previa, no se otorgar\\u00e1 reembolso.<\\/li><li><strong>Reservas completadas:<\\/strong> Una vez que una reserva se haya completado con \\u00e9xito, no se aplicar\\u00e1n reembolsos.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>3. Tiempo de Procesamiento del Reembolso<\\/strong><\\/h4><ul><li>Los reembolsos aprobados se procesar\\u00e1n dentro de <strong>7 a 14 d\\u00edas h\\u00e1biles<\\/strong> al m\\u00e9todo de pago original.<\\/li><li>Los tiempos de reembolso pueden variar seg\\u00fan el procesador de pago utilizado (PayPal, CoinGate, QRPay, Tatum, Stripe, Flutterwave, SSLCOMMERZ, Razorpay, Perfect Money).<\\/li><li>Los usuarios recibir\\u00e1n un correo de confirmaci\\u00f3n una vez que el reembolso haya sido procesado.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>4. C\\u00f3mo Solicitar un Reembolso<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Para solicitar un reembolso, los usuarios deben:<\\/p><ul><li>Contactar a nuestro equipo de soporte a <strong>[Su Email de Soporte]<\\/strong> dentro de <strong>[X] d\\u00edas<\\/strong> a partir de la fecha de la reserva.<\\/li><li>Proporcionar el n\\u00famero de reserva y una raz\\u00f3n v\\u00e1lida para la solicitud de reembolso.<\\/li><li>Adjuntar documentos de respaldo si es necesario (ejemplo: prueba de cargos incorrectos o indisponibilidad del veh\\u00edculo).<\\/li><li>Nuestro equipo revisar\\u00e1 la solicitud y responder\\u00e1 en <strong>[X] d\\u00edas h\\u00e1biles<\\/strong>.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>5. Cambios en Esta Pol\\u00edtica<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>CarBo se reserva el derecho de modificar o actualizar esta pol\\u00edtica de reembolsos en cualquier momento. Cualquier cambio se comunicar\\u00e1 por correo electr\\u00f3nico o notificaciones en la plataforma.<\\/p><h4><strong>6. Cont\\u00e1ctanos<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Para consultas relacionadas con reembolsos, comun\\u00edcate con nosotros en:<br>\\ud83d\\udce7 <strong>support@carbo.com<\\/strong><br>\\ud83d\\udccd <strong>123 CarBo Street, Cityville, Country<\\/strong><\\/p>"},"ar":{"content":"<p>\\u0641\\u064a CarBo\\u060c \\u0646\\u0633\\u0639\\u0649 \\u062c\\u0627\\u0647\\u062f\\u064a\\u0646 \\u0644\\u062a\\u0648\\u0641\\u064a\\u0631 \\u062a\\u062c\\u0631\\u0628\\u0629 \\u062d\\u062c\\u0632 \\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0631\\u0627\\u062a \\u0633\\u0644\\u0633\\u0629 \\u0648\\u0645\\u0648\\u062b\\u0648\\u0642\\u0629 \\u0644\\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u062a\\u062e\\u062f\\u0645\\u064a\\u0646 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0628\\u0627\\u0626\\u0639\\u064a\\u0646. \\u062a\\u0648\\u0636\\u062d \\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0633\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u0631\\u062f\\u0627\\u062f \\u0647\\u0630\\u0647 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0634\\u0631\\u0648\\u0637 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u064a \\u064a\\u0645\\u0643\\u0646 \\u0641\\u064a\\u0647\\u0627 \\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u0631\\u062f\\u0627\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0628\\u0627\\u0644\\u063a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u062f\\u0641\\u0648\\u0639\\u0629 \\u0644\\u0644\\u062d\\u062c\\u0648\\u0632\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u064a \\u062a\\u062a\\u0645 \\u0639\\u0628\\u0631 \\u0645\\u0646\\u0635\\u062a\\u0646\\u0627. \\u0628\\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u062e\\u062f\\u0627\\u0645 CarBo\\u060c \\u0641\\u0625\\u0646\\u0643 \\u062a\\u0648\\u0627\\u0641\\u0642 \\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0647\\u0630\\u0647 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0633\\u0629.<\\/p><h4><strong>1. \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u0647\\u0644\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0644\\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u0631\\u062f\\u0627\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u0645\\u0648\\u0627\\u0644<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>\\u064a\\u0645\\u0643\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u0631\\u062f\\u0627\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0628\\u0644\\u063a \\u0641\\u064a \\u0627\\u0644\\u062d\\u0627\\u0644\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0627\\u0644\\u064a\\u0629:<\\/p><ul><li><strong>\\u0625\\u0644\\u063a\\u0627\\u0621 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062d\\u062c\\u0632 \\u0645\\u0646 \\u0642\\u0628\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0628\\u0627\\u0626\\u0639:<\\/strong> \\u0625\\u0630\\u0627 \\u0642\\u0627\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0628\\u0627\\u0626\\u0639 \\u0628\\u0625\\u0644\\u063a\\u0627\\u0621 \\u062d\\u062c\\u0632 \\u0645\\u0624\\u0643\\u062f\\u060c \\u064a\\u062d\\u0642 \\u0644\\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u062a\\u062e\\u062f\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u0631\\u062f\\u0627\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0628\\u0644\\u063a \\u0628\\u0627\\u0644\\u0643\\u0627\\u0645\\u0644.<\\/li><li><strong>\\u0639\\u062f\\u0645 \\u062a\\u0648\\u0641\\u0631 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0631\\u0629:<\\/strong> \\u0625\\u0630\\u0627 \\u0644\\u0645 \\u062a\\u0643\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0633\\u064a\\u0627\\u0631\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u062d\\u062c\\u0648\\u0632\\u0629 \\u0645\\u062a\\u0627\\u062d\\u0629 \\u0641\\u064a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0648\\u0642\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u062d\\u062f\\u062f \\u0648\\u0644\\u0645 \\u064a\\u062a\\u0645 \\u062a\\u0648\\u0641\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0628\\u062f\\u064a\\u0644 \\u0645\\u0646\\u0627\\u0633\\u0628\\u060c \\u064a\\u0645\\u0643\\u0646 \\u0644\\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u062a\\u062e\\u062f\\u0645 \\u0637\\u0644\\u0628 \\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u0631\\u062f\\u0627\\u062f.<\\/li><li><strong>\\u0623\\u062e\\u0637\\u0627\\u0621 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062f\\u0641\\u0639:<\\/strong> \\u0641\\u064a \\u062d\\u0627\\u0644\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062f\\u0641\\u0639 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0643\\u0631\\u0631 \\u0623\\u0648 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0631\\u0633\\u0648\\u0645 \\u063a\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0635\\u062d\\u064a\\u062d\\u0629 \\u0628\\u0633\\u0628\\u0628 \\u0623\\u062e\\u0637\\u0627\\u0621 \\u0641\\u064a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0646\\u0638\\u0627\\u0645\\u060c \\u064a\\u0645\\u0643\\u0646 \\u0644\\u0644\\u0645\\u0633\\u062a\\u062e\\u062f\\u0645\\u064a\\u0646 \\u0637\\u0644\\u0628 \\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u0631\\u062f\\u0627\\u062f.<\\/li><li><strong>\\u0641\\u0634\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0639\\u0627\\u0645\\u0644\\u0629:<\\/strong> \\u0625\\u0630\\u0627 \\u062a\\u0645 \\u062e\\u0635\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0628\\u0644\\u063a \\u0648\\u0644\\u0643\\u0646 \\u0644\\u0645 \\u064a\\u062a\\u0645 \\u062a\\u0623\\u0643\\u064a\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u062d\\u062c\\u0632\\u060c \\u0641\\u0633\\u064a\\u062a\\u0645 \\u0627\\u0633\\u062a\\u0631\\u062f\\u0627\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0628\\u0644\\u063a.<\\/li><\\/ul><p>\\ud83d\\udce7 <strong>support@carbo.com<\\/strong><br>\\ud83d\\udccd <strong>123 CarBo Street, Cityville, Country<\\/strong><\\/p>"}}}','status' => '1','editable' => '1','created_at' => '2023-08-10 20:19:01','updated_at' => '2025-02-21 09:54:15')
        );

        UsefulLink::insert($useful_links);
